{"tid":1427134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗今次大獲，推比二百萬人同所有發夢前線睇！","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:46:53.000Z","uid":259519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"678c7d61603b924424cc737c803720e6f50fa96f","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n整個「運動」已經發展左差不多兩個月，勇武、和理非、罷工、不合作，好多野我地都做過，政府從未正面回應過我地既訴求，反而係不斷遊花園、將個波拋去比警察（狗），製造示威者係暴徒破壞社會安寧既假像；<span style=\"color: gold;\">「從來令到香港社會亂既係當權者，唔係反抗者。社會大眾要考慮要反思既係點解有咁大既壓迫？你點會去指責一D被壓迫既人，而唔係去指責壓迫人既政權呢？呢個係絕對講唔過去？」</span><br />\n<br />\n但係我地必需要反思同認清我地作為香港人要追求既野係咩，最終目標係邊到，我自己覺得就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民主</span>。<br />\n<br />\nJoseph Schumpeter&rsquo;s definition:<br />\n   &ldquo;that institutional arrangement for arriving  at political decisions in which individuals acquire the power to decide <span style=\"color: red;\">by means of a competitive struggle for the people&rsquo;s vote&rdquo;<br />\n</span><br />\nFreedom House&rsquo;s electoral democracy:<br />\n   <span style=\"color: red;\">A political system that guarantees universal    adult suffrage</span> and whose leaders are elected in competitive multi-party and multi-candidate processes in which opposition parties have a legitimate chance of attaining power or participating in power<br />\n<br />\n我唔接受任何假普選，而係五大訴求其中一個 &mdash; 雙普選。<span style=\"color: gold;\">只要我地民選政府先能夠代表到大部分既香港人</span>，以市民利益為先而制定既政策，針對性解決香港問題：從醫療、樓價、交通、城市規劃等各個不同範疇既根本問題。<br />\n<br />\n但過程係需要我地團結一致去爭取。楊岳橋最近係BBC都講過 &ldquo;We are united&hellip;&rdquo; &ldquo;universal suffrage &ldquo;都提及過好多次，我相信都係好多香港人想要既野。<br />\n<br />\nThree stages of democratisation:<br />\n1. authoritarian regime ends （777政府）<br />\n2. democratic regime（由1124開始）<br />\n3. The consolidation of the democratic regime （1124後續）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSeymour Martin Lipset&rsquo;s modernisation theory:<br />\n&ldquo;The more well-to-do a nation, the greater the chances<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> it will sustain democracy</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nFour processes: Urbanisation, industrialisation, educational attainment, wealth generation<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1.Economic growth &gt;&gt; <br />\n2.social mobilisation &gt;&gt; <br />\n3.political mobilisation &gt;&gt; <br />\n4.regime change</span><br />\n<br />\n根據現時香港既整體環境，我認為上述既modernization theory入面既4個processes我地只係得&rdquo;economic growth&rdquo; 咁你會問，都無2&amp;3，點樣先做到第4樣野：有我地既民選政府？我再一次引用楊岳橋係BBC入面講 &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">history is history</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">過去既歷史就由佢成為歷史，同時我地亦不應被過去既成功作為現時和未來既標準，更不應因為歷史而被制肘住我地發展中既運動，要做既係團結一致，創造歷史&mdash; </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1.Economic growth <br />\n2.Regime change<br />\n3.Political mobilization <br />\n4.Social mobilization</span> <br />\n<br />\n而非上面原始既modernization theory！"},{"pid":"4909be4455d97eda0ac2449c0c1b05610a922761","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"下面各國係依啲年份都有大事發生過，詳情唔講，自己上網睇，但我想指出既係世界各地都不斷演變，追求民主，依一樣野係普世價值黎，香港亦都係要尋求改變。<br />\n<br />\nPhilippines 1986<br />\nSouth Korea 1987<br />\nPakistan 1988<br />\n(Myanmar) 1988<br />\n(China) 1989<br />\n(Malaysia) 1998<br />\n(Iran) 2002<br />\nEast Germany 1989<br />\nCzechoslovakia 1989<br />\nRomania 1989<br />\nNepal 1990<br />\nBangladesh 1991<br />\nThailand 1992<br />\nIndonesia 1998<br />\nSerbia 2000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">General pattern of democratization</span> <br />\nThreat and Grievances （社會被壓迫）<br />\nMoral outrage（政府同警察既回應及行為）<br />\nSupport from economic and communal elites （200萬+5+所有支持者）<br />\n<br />\n然後下面⋯⋯<br />\n&ldquo;According to moral principles, a government that assumes or retains power through fraudulent means <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">has no moral basis</span></span>&hellip;If such a government does not itself freely correct the evil it has inflicted on the people, then<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> it is our serious moral obligation as a people to make it do so</span></span>&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依篇野並唔係任何行動計劃，戰術建議<br />\n我係要話比你地知，五大訴求，缺一不可，香港人要團結一致，創造歷史！雖然一國兩制五十年不變，但歷史係歷史，不獨立係仲可以有一個出路：永續港人治港，高度自治。好多人都覺得97後50年，就會失去現時香港既自由，無人諗過其實一國兩制可以一百年？二百年？永續特區行政區？所有野靠我地爭取，但短期目標係五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依排見身邊好多人有絕對同放棄既念頭<br />\n但<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加油！</span></span><br />\n我上次搭完校巴，有個同學仔同我講，佢都係一樣會堅持到底，直到成功。"},{"pid":"9fda6da3ad56090a617da83b094f27fea7e13a2e","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"dc17f9f92f651eb12086368bf5031a91e0d30e02","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"403e27e31a2ee5f013c3765707f111695be8b55e","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"88001630520ad79ae0b50d66dd552210a4608717","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"bed00659b60683536d0f7dead7b67c384326ddd6","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"796c83fcb62254b9556c9d3917a256f900cbf6ca","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"380fd540d794fe67675584b8a177e3c0f4b0a579","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"32c0958ea3f849e14507a3a5ce02a53bdaa11ede","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"5b8def377a80f41cef2be9f5d881623c173b7b5a","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"360347b084cb505202649142dbbd7894b5fd85af","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"a446afa60ae84865d9c1bcd81926a3b20e9bad58","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"訴"},{"pid":"ba02654ff8cc92a38441e5df3a6d9c42325ef4ae","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"求"},{"pid":"00e5ce120001f65191e0e2f804b95faf5005f91d","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"缺"},{"pid":"8d0c76f9ae8ac2021ea421689c9752245733d76f","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"340cd92e518536981b28b98ffa0eb2fd2ed354fc","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"不"},{"pid":"264c4699014f15096f2f2fabb7b6924c3352f4d9","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"可"},{"pid":"5ffac6b08204be5a4d9ddd957aac8c5beaef6f70","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"成"},{"pid":"095bdd6716f6b23ffd7157e9d0a72bd9be15641c","tid":1427134,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"立"},{"pid":"b239796e7678ce82c799d50909bc6e5eaf9f8f8a","tid":1427134,"uid":300478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf59637443